{"type":null,"faqId":31817,"title":"如何省电？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>开启省电模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“设置 &gt; 省电管理”，勾选一种省电模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>不使用手机时，请按电源键关闭屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>缩短屏幕待机时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; 休眠”，选择较短的屏幕待机时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98890\" style=\"width:5.165278in;height:2.4590278in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p  >\n <span>降低屏幕亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; 亮度”，拖动滑块降低屏幕亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-2</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98891\" style=\"width:5.165278in;height:2.4305556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p  >\n <span>使用耳机拨打电话、听音乐等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>不需要使用蓝牙时，请关闭蓝牙功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-3</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98892\" style=\"width:3.325in;height:2.8090277in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p  >\n <span>不需要使用无线局域网时，请关闭无线局域网连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-4</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98893\" style=\"width:3.3319445in;height:2.8097222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p  >\n <span>不需要使用GPS服务时，请关闭GPS功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-5</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98894\" style=\"width:3.3270833in;height:2.8138888in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98895\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6337","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287935000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":118,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"省电,节省电量,延长待机时间,延长使用时间","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}